data.title: Windows Server 2003 - Microsoft Lifecycle
data.meta_description: Windows Server 2003  follows the Fixed Lifecycle Policy.
data.text:
Windows Server 2003

Windows Server 2003 follows the Fixed Lifecycle Policy.

This applies to the following editions: Datacenter (32-bit x86), Datacenter (x64), Datacenter for Itanium-Based Systems, Enterprise (32-Bit x86), Enterprise for Itanium-based Systems, Enterprise X64, Standard (32-bit x86), Web

Support dates are shown in the Pacific Time Zone (PT) - Redmond, WA, USA.
